{"tid":346242,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"脆弱雞翼嚟講，翼定鎚正啲？","createTime":"2017-08-03T19:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T15:16:28.000Z","uid":10521,"like":973,"dislike":302,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f40350f3f92e10bdd6047a869d61250ba9e1d357","tid":346242,"uid":10521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:06:21.000Z","msg":"今日同朋友食嘅時候講起呢個話題，佢話鎚正啲，啖啖肉又可以一隻手食。<br />\n但我就話翼一定正好多，每一次啲肉都係咁多汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，鎚好多時啲肉都係鞋，更何況食得雞翼怕咩整污糟手，正所謂骨邊肉賽神仙，兩隻手食先係最滋味嘅食法。如果成盒四隻都係翼一定好賣好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，各位巴絲打點睇？<br />\n<br />\n翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鎚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上J圖一幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/030542_05d3a96b64cc0f7d91204a8249edcc07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F030542_05d3a96b64cc0f7d91204a8249edcc07.jpg&h=1a9adc12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4ccf9fe9c4b3ed86f78bf7efc2d638421770c3a","tid":346242,"uid":17081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5452cbe15a4c7bec9478c08690997aa2ccc16ee","tid":346242,"uid":78426,"like":414,"dislike":5,"score":409,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:09:38.000Z","msg":"巴打，你係唔係唔知其實係可以嗌全翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc65c008c2a874ab10ca63320531697b968d5ee","tid":346242,"uid":91014,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:10:17.000Z","msg":"翼都可以一隻手食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3932e3332d4b4a6b241dc191e52f8ce9d704b29","tid":346242,"uid":59687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"c